                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18041024-4-off22 t18041024-4-cd23"></join>, four shawls, value 10 s. and a half-shawl, value 6 d. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18041024-4-victim68" type="victimName">
                        Thomas-Perry 
                        Tuther
